com.here.android.mpa.mapping

Class MapModelObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.android.mpa.common.ViewObject
      • com.here.android.mpa.mapping.MapObject
        • com.here.android.mpa.mapping.MapModelObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MapGeoModel, MapLocalModel

    public class MapModelObject
extends MapObject
    Base class for MapLocalModel and MapGeoModel. This class provides additional functionalities to set lighting and material properties to a model object.
